# PATCH: 0033-repo-scaffold
# WHY: Repo local moi tao (0008) trong tron -> user khong biet bat dau tu dau. Can co san README +
#      folder mau (scripts/playbooks/deploys) de dinh huong.
# WHAT: quickwin_gitea.go: sau CreateRepo chay NEN (goroutine + ctx rieng 60s) scaffoldRepo() PutFile
#       README.md + scripts/ + playbooks/ + deploys/ (dung PutFile 0029). Async de khong chan tao
#       project (Gitea lanh commit cham). Non-fatal, chi log neu fail.
# SPEC: docs/L2-specs/core-patches/0033-repo-scaffold.md
# BASELINE: v2.18.16
#
diff --git a/api/projects/quickwin_gitea.go b/api/projects/quickwin_gitea.go
